data.description: JUST APPRAISED FOR $309K! Back on the market due to buyer financing falling through. Gorgeous 3 bedroom Oakleaf home with a BRAND NEW ROOF! Open floor plan with luxury vinyl plank flooring throughout - NO carpet! Split bedrooms with the primary bedroom suite in the rear of the home. Kitchen is spacious with a breakfast nook, laundry closet and pantry. Screened back patio perfect for relaxing after a long day. Easy maintenance backyard with pavers and an irrigation system already installed! Two car garage and fully fenced backyard. Access to the AMAZING resort style Oakleaf Plantation amenities, including swim parks, fitness centers, walking trails, tennis, basketball courts & soccer and football fields and more! Zoned for highly desired Clay County schools. Great location close to Oakleaf Town Center shopping, restaurants and 295 for an easy commute!
